name: LOT Polish Airlines Boeing 787-8 SP-LRE Delivery Flight takeoff from Paine Field
description:
Dedicated to TheSamoloot! Check out his channel here: www.youtube.com/thesamoloot
Hey everyone, this is the delivery flight of LOT Polish Airline's fifth 787 departing Paine Field for Warsaw, Poland (EPWA/WAW). This was shot with a DSLR camera, which is meant for pictures, so the quality isn't the same as my normal spotting videos. Sorry for the shakiness as well. I hope you'll still enjoy it!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
